Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:57.52,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,So you did come!{E:So you came for me.} \N Thank you!{E:Thanks for that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:01:01.83,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Since you’ve been such a good girl, \N I’ll let you in on something good.{E:Since you've been a good girl, I think I'll give you something I've been keeping.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:03.08,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:09.17,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,This is the tale passed down \N by our ancestors, the Meteor Tribe.{E:They're the tales that have been passed down by my ancestors, the Draconids}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:16.22,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,And now, \N I’ll pass our history on to you!{E:And now...I will pass that history and lore on to you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:32.99,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,A thousand years ago, \N an enormous meteor struck this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:52.61,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Natural energy from deep beneath Hoenn \N poured out onto the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:02:00.74,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Primally Reverted Groudon and Kaiogre \N fought endless, furious clashes over that energy.{E:Primal Groudon and Primal Kyogre fought over that energy in endless, furious clashes.}{E:Thirsting for that energy, Primal Kyogre and Primal Groudon once again woke.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.80,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,The people could do nothing.{E:people could do nothing.}{people here = humans}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.61,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Nothing but wait for the danger to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:50.96,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,And so, the people prayed, \N hoping for salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:58.22,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Praying for the appearance of the \N scintillating emerald Legendary Pokémon... Rekkuuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:05.83,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Then, the prayers bound \N the people and the Pokémon together...{E:Yet this wish bound people and Pokémon together,}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.80,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,...and the Pokémon \N changed its shape!{E:enabling the Legendary Pokémon to change its appearance...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.68,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,It’s just like \N Mega Evolution, right?{It looks just like Mega Evolution, right?!}{E:It sounds like Mega Evolution, doesn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:37.66,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Primal Groudon and Primal Kaiogre \N vanished into the depths of land and sea,{E:the two vanished into the depths of land and sea.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.70,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,and peace returned to the world.{E:peace returned to the world.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:50.19,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,After that, to worship Rekkuuza \N and the rainbow stone that created that power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:53.75,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,our ancestors \N built this enormous tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:37.71,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,The Meteor Tribe prophesied \N that another meteor{meteoroid} would fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.97,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Even more enormous \N than the previous two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.63,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Large enough \N to destroy the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:53.69,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,I asked myself, \N what could I do to protect the most people?{E:I spent a long time thinking about how I could protect the happiness of as many people as possible.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:58.32,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,As my fate, for carrying both \N power and knowledge...{E:What I must do, as one who holds both the knowledge and the power...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.78,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Now, our story is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.54,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Welcome to Dragonhark Altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.48,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,A new tale will begin right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.91,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Ever since I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:20.30,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,whenever I felt like the weight on my shoulders \N was so heavy it would crush me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:24.46,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,I... would always \N gaze at the stars.{E:Ever since I was a little girl, I have always turned my eyes up to the sky.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.74,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,You understand \N what I’m about to do, don’t you?{E:You know what I am trying to do here by now, don't you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:37.61,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,I will summon Rekkuuza with the Key Stones \N and destroy the meteor heading for Hoenn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.33,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,That is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.31,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,If something happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.44,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,...take care of her.{E:If something happens to me... Please... Take this little one...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.85,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Now then... \N Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.23,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Rekkuuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.38,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Hear my prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.90,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Show me your true form!{E:Show me your true face!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.92,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Hey! Show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:59.30,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,It can’t be... \N After everything I’ve done...{E:Everything...I've done...till now...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.28,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,After everything, {\i1}Rekkuuza{\i0} \N was the one not strong enough?{E:The one without enough power...is you, Rayquaza?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.66,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,I never considered...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.42,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,That meteorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.97,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.17,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,A Mega Stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:44.61,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Our Guardian God, Rekkuuza, \N chose you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.10,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,...instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.74,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Do it! Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.52,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.71,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,And... This is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:38.02,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,This is the last of our legacy \N to pass along.{E:That is my final... The final duty of the last Lorekeeper of the Draconid people!}{Anime line is kinda garbled and pointless, but JP games had 'This is my... This is _the Meteor tribe_'s last thing to pass on.' - anime changed both groups to 'our'}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:06.75,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,Ever since I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.40,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,I would always...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.11,Main,Higana,0,0,0,,...gaze at the stars.
